  "cards": [
    {
      "id": "intro-0",
      "sectionId": "intro",
      "title": "Intro",
      "body": "This is a quick reference cheat sheet that lists the most useful features of [SASS](https://sass-lang.com)."
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-1",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "Introduction",
      "body": "• [Documentation](https://sass-lang.com/documentation) _(sass-lang.com)_\n• [Learn X in Y minutes](https://learnxinyminutes.com/docs/sass/) _(learnxinyminutes.com)_"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-2",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "Variables",
      "body": "```scss\n$defaultLinkColor: #46eac2;\n\na {\n  color: $defaultLinkColor;\n}\n```"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-3",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "String interpolation",
      "body": "```scss\n$wk: -webkit-;\n\n.rounded-box {\n  #{$wk}border-radius: 4px;\n}\n```"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-4",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "Comments",
      "body": "```scss\n/*\n Block comments\n Block comments\n Block comments\n*/\n\n// Line comments\n```"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-5",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "Mixins",
      "body": "```scss\n@mixin heading-font {\n  font-family: sans-serif;\n  font-weight: bold;\n}\nh1 {\n  @include heading-font;\n}\n```\n\nSee: [Mixins](#sass-mixins)"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-7",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "Nesting",
      "body": "```scss\n.markdown-body {\n  a {\n    color: blue;\n    &:hover {\n      color: red;\n    }\n  }\n}\n```"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-8",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "to properties",
      "body": "```scss\ntext: {\n  // like text-align: center\n  align: center;\n  // like text-transform: uppercase\n  transform: uppercase;\n}\n```"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-9",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "Extend",
      "body": "```scss\n.button {\n    ···\n}\n```\n\n```scss\n.push-button {\n  @extend .button;\n}\n```"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-10",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "%40import",
      "body": "%60%60%60scss%0A%40import%20'.%2Fother_sass_file'%3B%0A%40import%20'%2Fcode'%2C%20'lists'%3B%0A%0A%2F%2F%20Plain%20CSS%20%40imports%0A%40import%20'theme.css'%3B%0A%40import%20url(theme)%3B%0A%60%60%60%0A%0AThe%20%60.sass%60%20or%20%60.sass%60%20extension%20is%20optional.",
      "encoded": true
    },
    {
      "id": "s2-12",
      "sectionId": "s2",
      "title": "Parameters",
      "body": "```scss\n@mixin font-size($n) {\n  font-size: $n * 1.2em;\n}\n```\n\n```scss\nbody {\n  @include font-size(2);\n}\n```"
    },
    {
      "id": "s2-13",
      "sectionId": "s2",
      "title": "Default values",
      "body": "```scss\n@mixin pad($n: 10px) {\n  padding: $n;\n}\n```\n\n```scss\nbody {\n  @include pad(15px);\n}\n```"
    },
    {
      "id": "s2-14",
      "sectionId": "s2",
      "title": "Default variable",
      "body": "```scss\n$default-padding: 10px;\n\n@mixin pad($n: $default-padding) {\n  padding: $n;\n}\n\nbody {\n  @include pad(15px);\n}\n```"
    },
    {
      "id": "s3-15",
      "sectionId": "s3",
      "title": "rgba",
      "body": "```scss\nrgb(100, 120, 140)\nrgba(100, 120, 140, .5)\nrgba($color, .5)\n```"
    },
    {
      "id": "s3-16",
      "sectionId": "s3",
      "title": "Mixing",
      "body": "```scss\nmix($a, $b, 10%)   // 10% a, 90% b\n```"
    },
    {
      "id": "s3-17",
      "sectionId": "s3",
      "title": "Modifying HSLA",
      "body": "```scss\ndarken($color, 5%)\nlighten($color, 5%)\n```\n\n```scss\nsaturate($color, 5%)\ndesaturate($color, 5%)\ngrayscale($color)\n```\n\n```scss\nadjust-hue($color, 15deg)\ncomplement($color)    // like adjust-hue(_, 180deg)\ninvert($color)\n```\n\n```scss\nfade-in($color, .5)   // aka opacify()\nfade-out($color, .5)  // aka transparentize()\nrgba($color, .5)      // sets alpha to .5\n```"
    },
    {
      "id": "s3-18",
      "sectionId": "s3",
      "title": "Getting individual values - HSLA",
      "body": "```scss\nhue($color)         // 0deg..360deg\nsaturation($color)  // 0%..100%\nlightness($color)   // 0%..100%\nalpha($color)       // 0..1 (aka opacity())\n```"
    },
    {
      "id": "s3-19",
      "sectionId": "s3",
      "title": "RGB",
      "body": "```scss\nred($color)         // 0..255\ngreen($color)\nblue($color)\n```\n\nSee: [hue()](http://sass-lang.com/documentation/Sass/Script/Functions.html#hue-instance_method),\n[red()](http://sass-lang.com/documentation/Sass/Script/Functions.html#red-instance_method)"
    },
    {
      "id": "s3-21",
      "sectionId": "s3",
      "title": "Adjustments",
      "body": "```scss\n// Changes by fixed amounts\nadjust-color($color, $blue: 5)\nadjust-color($color, $lightness: -30%) // darken(_, 30%)\nadjust-color($color, $alpha: -0.4)     // fade-out(_, .4)\nadjust-color($color, $hue: 30deg)      // adjust-hue(_, 15deg)\n```\n\n```scss\n// Changes via percentage\nscale-color($color, $lightness: 50%)\n```\n\n```scss\n// Changes one property completely\nchange-color($color, $hue: 180deg)\nchange-color($color, $blue: 250)\n```\n\nSupported: `$red`, `$green`, `$blue`, `$hue`, `$saturation`, `$lightness`, `$alpha`"
    },
    {
      "id": "s4-23",
      "sectionId": "s4",
      "title": "Strings",
      "body": "%60%60%60scss%0Aunquote('hello')%0Aquote(hello)%0A%60%60%60%0A%0A%60%60%60scss%0Ato-upper-case(hello)%0Ato-lower-case(hello)%0A%60%60%60%0A%0A%60%60%60scss%0Astr-length(hello%20world)%0Astr-slice(hello%2C%202%2C%205)%20%20%20%20%20%2F%2F%20%22ello%22%20-%20it's%201-based%2C%20not%200-based%0Astr-insert(%22abcd%22%2C%20%22X%22%2C%201)%20%2F%2F%20%22Xabcd%22%0A%60%60%60",
      "encoded": true
    },
    {
      "id": "s4-24",
      "sectionId": "s4",
      "title": "Units",
      "body": "%60%60%60scss%0Aunit(3em)%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%2F%2F%20'em'%0Aunitless(100px)%20%20%2F%2F%20false%0A%60%60%60",
      "encoded": true
    },
    {
      "id": "s4-25",
      "sectionId": "s4",
      "title": "Numbers",
      "body": "```scss\nfloor(3.5)\nceil(3.5)\nround(3.5)\nabs(3.5)\n```\n\n```scss\nmin(1, 2, 3)\nmax(1, 2, 3)\n```\n\n```scss\npercentage(.5)   // 50%\nrandom(3)        // 0..3\n```"
    },
    {
      "id": "s4-26",
      "sectionId": "s4",
      "title": "Misc",
      "body": "%60%60%60scss%0Avariable-exists(red)%20%20%20%20%2F%2F%20checks%20for%20%24red%0Amixin-exists(red-text)%20%20%2F%2F%20checks%20for%20%40mixin%20red-text%0Afunction-exists(redify)%0A%60%60%60%0A%0A%60%60%60scss%0Aglobal-variable-exists(red)%0A%60%60%60%0A%0A%60%60%60scss%0Aselector-append('.menu'%2C%20'li'%2C%20'a')%20%20%20%2F%2F%20.menu%20li%20a%0Aselector-nest('.menu'%2C%20'%26%3Ahover%20li')%20%20%2F%2F%20.menu%3Ahover%20li%0Aselector-extend(...)%0Aselector-parse(...)%0Aselector-replace(...)%0Aselector-unify(...)%0A%60%60%60",
      "encoded": true
    },
    {
      "id": "s5-27",
      "sectionId": "s5",
      "title": "Feature check",
      "body": "```scss\nfeature-exists(global-variable-shadowing)\n```"
    },
    {
      "id": "s5-28",
      "sectionId": "s5",
      "title": "Features",
      "body": "• global-variable-shadowing\n• extend-selector-pseudoclass\n• units-level-3\n• at-error"
    },
    {
      "id": "s6-29",
      "sectionId": "s6",
      "title": "For loops",
      "body": "```scss\n@for $i from 1 through 4 {\n  .item-#{$i} {\n    left: 20px * $i;\n  }\n}\n```"
    },
    {
      "id": "s6-30",
      "sectionId": "s6",
      "title": "Each%20loops%20(simple)",
      "body": "%60%60%60scss%0A%24menu-items%3A%20home%20about%20contact%3B%0A%0A%40each%20%24item%20in%20%24menu-items%20%7B%0A%20%20.photo-%23%7B%24item%7D%20%7B%0A%20%20%20%20background%3A%20url('%23%7B%24item%7D.jpg')%3B%0A%20%20%7D%0A%7D%0A%60%60%60",
      "encoded": true
    },
    {
      "id": "s6-31",
      "sectionId": "s6",
      "title": "Each%20loops%20(nested)",
      "body": "%60%60%60scss%0A%24backgrounds%3A%20(home%2C%20'home.jpg')%2C%20(about%2C%20'about.jpg')%3B%0A%0A%40each%20%24id%2C%20%24image%20in%20%24backgrounds%20%7B%0A%20%20.photo-%23%7B%24id%7D%20%7B%0A%20%20%20%20background%3A%20url(%24image)%3B%0A%20%20%7D%0A%7D%0A%60%60%60",
      "encoded": true
    },
    {
      "id": "s6-32",
      "sectionId": "s6",
      "title": "While loops",
      "body": "```scss\n$i: 6;\n@while $i > 0 {\n  .item-#{$i} {\n    width: 2em * $i;\n  }\n  $i: $i - 2;\n}\n```"
    },
    {
      "id": "s7-33",
      "sectionId": "s7",
      "title": "Conditionals",
      "body": "%60%60%60scss%0A%40if%20%24position%20%3D%3D%20'left'%20%7B%0A%20%20position%3A%20absolute%3B%0A%20%20left%3A%200%3B%0A%7D%20%40else%20if%20%24position%20%3D%3D%20'right'%20%7B%0A%20%20position%3A%20absolute%3B%0A%20%20right%3A%200%3B%0A%7D%20%40else%20%7B%0A%20%20position%3A%20static%3B%0A%7D%0A%60%60%60",
      "encoded": true
    },
    {
      "id": "s7-34",
      "sectionId": "s7",
      "title": "Interpolation",
      "body": "%60%60%60scss%0A.%23%7B%24klass%7D%20%7B%20...%20%7D%20%20%20%20%20%20%2F%2F%20Class%0Acall(%24function-name)%20%20%20%20%2F%2F%20Functions%0A%0A%40media%20%23%7B%24tablet%7D%0Afont%3A%20%23%7B%24size%7D%2F%23%7B%24line-height%7D%0Aurl(%22%23%7B%24background%7D.jpg%22)%0A%60%60%60",
      "encoded": true
